(19942, 1, '2015-04-14 07:09:00', '2015-04-14 07:09:00', 'Headquartered in Atlanta, GA, Chime Solutions creates effortless customer care experiences for clients across industries. From customer care to seasonal and BPO support services, our experienced team delivers quality service via our cloud-based customer platform.\r\n\r\nAt Chime Solutions, we lead with remarkable customer experience, answering the call for excellence every time, right here in the U.S.  From our 68,000 square foot call center, our leadership team brings over 75 years of collective experience in the contact center and support industry.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2015-04-29 09:18:13', '2015-04-29 09:18:13', '', 0, 'http://wordpress.iworklab.com/chime/?page_id=19942', 0, 'page', '', 0),
