(19948, 1, '2015-04-14 07:10:20', '2015-04-14 07:10:20', 'Low operational costs, high customer satisfaction and effortless customer care experiences are essential elements to any business. At Chime Solutions, we provide turn-key Business Process Outsourcing (BPO) solutions for clients that includes call handling, quality assurance, workforce management, interactive voice solutions and CRM functionality.\r\n\r\nOur team understands the value of end-to-end program analytics for ongoing measurement and reporting, and the importance of creating a culture of continuous coaching for improved ROI and program results. From back office support to help desk to appointment setting, Chime Solutions enables our clients to efficiently streamline customer experiences.', 'bpo', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bpo', '', '', '2015-04-17 09:48:24', '2015-04-17 09:48:24', '', 19940, 'http://wordpress.iworklab.com/chime/?page_id=19948', 0, 'page', '', 0),
