(19950, 1, '2015-04-14 07:10:39', '2015-04-14 07:10:39', 'Our call centers strive to deliver superior customer care through each customer interaction. The quality of service on the other end of the phone influences how your customers view your company. Our high-quality customer care solutions, combined with decades of experience, have been proven to  promote customer satisfaction, loyalty and ultimately, profitability. \r\n\r\nAs the face of your brand, call center representatives play a critical role in your company. That is why we only hire the best through our culture of excellence, and train each individual on site, in our 68,000-foot headquarters in Atlanta, GA. Specializing in call center management, customer service, inbound/outbound calls, and product and technical support, we drive business value. It’s our job to deliver high-quality support and customer care solutions.', 'Customer Care', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'customer-care', '', '', '2015-04-17 10:22:53', '2015-04-17 10:22:53', '', 19940, 'http://wordpress.iworklab.com/chime/?page_id=19950', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(19951, 1, '2015-04-14 07:10:39', '2015-04-14 07:10:39', '', 'Customer Care', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19950-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-14 07:10:39', '2015-04-14 07:10:39', '', 19950, 'http://wordpress.iworklab.com/chime/?p=19951', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(19953, 1, '2015-04-14 07:11:04', '2015-04-14 07:11:04', 'Responsive, helpful customer support is our business any time of the year. As fluctuations in your company occur, we’re here to provide the customer care necessary to sustain growth, and answer your customers’ calls. We are able to ramp up or ramp down as needed. With an expansive, 68,000-foot call center in Atlanta, GA, we strive to be always on and reliable as we act as an extension of our clients’ customer relationships.\r\n\r\nBy partnering with Chime Solutions, you will have access to a group of highly trained professionals powered by state-of-the art technology. We provide seamless customer support, as we strive to resolve all issues on the first call, to enable operational efficiencies.  We believe superior customer experiences win loyalty, and greater strengthen customer relationships. In short, we’re always on, so you don’t have to be.', 'Seasonal Support', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'seasonal-support', '', '', '2015-04-17 10:15:38', '2015-04-17 10:15:38', '', 19940, 'http://wordpress.iworklab.com/chime/?page_id=19953', 0, 'page', '', 0),
